      "type": "action",
      "pdf_page": 2,
      "display_page": 1,
      "source": "Rain hammers the windows. MARA, 30s, logs the",
      "translation": "雨点狠狠砸在窗户上。__玛拉__，三十多岁，借着灯光记录着"
